This project came about largely due to my frustration at the expense of miniature trolling motors, and having a basic kayak, I wanted a hands-free control system.
<br/>
<img src='/images/TMFullConfig.png'>
<br/>
For now, I have decided on a 1:1 gear ratio, but may experiment with variations if the turning radius does not fit my needs.
